OL,3,CTeacher banned indefinitely after
OL,4,Cclaiming Covid fake and Islam 'demonic'
OL,6,FMost of the allegations included
OL,7,Frelate to Lawler's time as a history
OL,8,Fteacher at Bede Academy, in
OL,9,FNorthumberland, from 2015-20, the
OL,10,FLocal Democracy Reporting Service
OL,11,Freports.
OL,13,FThe 62-year-old falsely told Year 6
OL,14,Fstudents during a transition day to
OL,15,Fsecondary school that Rosa Parks had
OL,16,Fnot existed, that the famous account
OL,17,Fof the Black activist giving up her
OL,18,Fseat on a bus was 'staged', and that
OL,19,FMartin Luther King was a "fraud and
OL,20,Fhad embezzled lots of money", it was
OL,21,Ffound.
