OL,3,CTeacher banned indefinitely after
OL,4,Cclaiming Covid fake and Islam 'demonic'
OL,6,FDespite receiving a warning letter in
OL,7,F2019 about his controversial views, he
OL,8,Fwent on to be employed as a supply
OL,9,Fteacher by Monarch Education
OL,10,FRecruitment Agency in Bristol and
OL,11,Fworked at Bristol Brunel Academy in
OL,12,FSpeedwell, part of Cabot Learning
OL,13,FFederation.
OL,15,FThe TRA panel, whose findings were
OL,16,Fpublished on Monday 5 January, said
OL,17,Fthe teacher told Bristol pupils in
OL,18,FSeptember 2022 that there was no
OL,19,Fscientific proof of Covid-19.
