OL,6,FThe panel decided that Lawler was
OL,7,Fguilty of unacceptable professional
OL,8,Fconduct that could bring the
OL,9,Fprofession into disrepute.
OL,11,FThe report said he authored or co-
OL,12,Fauthored an article in 2015 in an
OL,13,Fonline Catholic newsletter called The
OL,14,FFlock that said "Catholicism is the
OL,15,Fone true religion and... all other
OL,16,Freligions are false, and of all the
OL,17,Ffalse religions Islam is demonstrably
OL,18,Fthe most demonic".
