OL,6,FThe piece added that "anal copulation
OL,7,Fbetween two men is an unnatural,
OL,8,Funhealthy, disgusting perversion",
OL,9,F"killing children in the womb by
OL,10,Fabortion is a great wickedness" and
OL,11,Fthat Islam was "Satanically inspired'.
OL,13,FThe TRA concluded that the teacher
OL,14,Ftold Bede Academy pupils in December
OL,15,F2020 that "back in the day you used to
OL,16,Fbe able to get cocaine purer", a
OL,17,Fcomment that was "in no way related to
OL,18,Fthe lesson".
