OL,6,FIt decided Lawler should be banned
OL,7,Ffrom the profession indefinitely with
OL,8,Fa minimum of four years before he
OL,9,Fcould apply to be reinstated as there
OL,10,Fwas a "high risk of similar misconduct
OL,11,Freoccurring".
OL,13,FConfirming the ruling, a civil servant
OL,14,Fon behalf of the Secretary of State
OL,15,Fwrote: "The panel finds that the
OL,16,Fconduct of Mr Lawler fell
OL,17,Fsignificantly short of the standards
OL,18,Fexpected of the profession.
