OL,6,F"The findings of misconduct are
OL,7,Fserious as they include a teacher
OL,8,Fengaging in behaviour that sought to
OL,9,Fadvance his own personal, often
OL,10,Fcontroversial, viewpoints over others,
OL,11,Fand reduce the standing of his own
OL,12,Fpupils.
OL,14,F"Patrick Lawler is prohibited from
OL,15,Fteaching indefinitely and cannot teach
OL,16,Fin any school, sixth-form college,
OL,17,Frelevant youth accommodation or
OL,18,Fchildren's home in England."
OL,20,FLawler did not attend the hearing and
OL,21,Fwas not represented.
